The complete overview of this learning of Spring Security:

1. CSRF
    In this concept we have the capability to manage the authorization phase to restrict
    based on the session handling , maintain the session stateless and same site strict.

2. Bcrypt
    This the method which helps to store the users password in cyber script with the help
    of its interface , class and methods.
    Also AuthenticationProvider(DaoAuthenticationProvider) is helps to handle the authentication.

3. JWT (JSON Web Token)
    AuthenticationManager is helps to handle the verification process with users stored
    in the database with the current request.